final_desc: - - Lobster karang dan udang laut besar lainnya (Palinurus spp., Panulirus spp.,Jasus spp.) :Krustasea, berkulit maupun tidak, hidup, segar, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam; krustasea diasapi, dimasak maupun tidak sebelum atau selama proses pengasapan; krustasea, berkulit, dikukus atau direbus, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam maupun tidak; tepung, tepung kasar dan pellet dari krustasea, layak untuk dikonsumsi manusia.;- - Rock lobster and other sea crawfish (Palinurus spp., Panulirus spp., Jasus spp.) :Crustaceans, whether in shell or not, live, fresh, chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; smoked crustaceans, whether in shell or not, whether or not cooked before or during the smoking process; crustaceans, in shell, cooked by steaming or by boiling in water, whether or not chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; flours, meals and pellets of crustaceans, fit for human consumption.;- - - Livers- - - Hati
